I still remember watching Gaurav Taneja (Flying Beast) with my family, and it was through him that I discovered @myproteinin 🚀

Starting supplementation with My Protein marked a turning point for me. The world of fitness influencers and sponsorships encouraged me, igniting a dream to become a part of that community. As a student on a tight budget, I often found myself imagining the day I’d be a fitness influencer, proudly sponsored by a leading brand.

Cut to 3.5 years of relentless training, and one morning, I woke up to a text message from My Protein. The excitement was beyond words. A brand I had admired and trusted had recognized my efforts and wanted to collaborate. 
My Protein, with its Informed-Sport certification and ISO 9001, GMP, and HACCP accreditations, stands out as one of the best supplement brands in the market. 💪

Whether you’re just starting out or you’re a seasoned athlete, My Protein can help you achieve remarkable results. And now, I’m thrilled to offer you an exclusive discount code “YUVRAJMP.” ❤️‍🔥
Use this code at checkout to save extra, and join me on this incredible fitness journey. Your support means the world to me as I continue to grow as an athlete.
